	<h3>Merliot Hub Demo</h3>
	<h4>Introduction</h4>
	<p>This is a demo of Merliot Hub, a private device hub.  The devices are running in demo mode, so they're not accessing real hardware, just simulating hardware.  The hub runs locally or on the cloud.</p>
	<p>Install your <b>own</b> hub with <b>real</b> devices using the guides below.</p>
	<p>Merliot hub is built with Go, TinyGo, and htmx.</p>
	<h4>Quick Start Using Docker</h4>
	<pre class="text-sm bg-gray-100 p-4">docker pull merliot/hub
docker run -p 80:8000 merliot/hub</pre>
